instructText: In this next part of the experiment, please recall each story to the best of your ability.

recall: Thomas and sadie enter a diner. thomas asks for a booth in the back, which the waiter allows. sadie begins to ask thomas about his day but he seems out of it. after taking some time, thomas says to sadie that he wants to take a break in their relationship so that he can focus on his career path. sadie is stunned. the waiter comes over and asks them what they would like. thomas and sadie hurridly order from the menu, thomas getting his regular and sadie getting a reuben. after the waiter leaves, sadie asks thomas if this is really what he wants. after the waiter comes back to give them both their food, sadie shakes the reuben in thomas's face and yells about the stuff she would like back from tom. sadie then storms out of the diner while thomas is left at the booth to contemplate.

James and teresa are at a new sushi place in town. upon entering, teresa bumps her head into the glass door, which everyone sees. she then sits at the bar, with james only one seat away. thomas decides to ask teresa if she was ok, and teresa responds with a grin. she tehn asks james if he has ever been stung by a scorpion. thomas thinks that teresa may have a concussion, and is confused about teresa's question. teresa then explains that she was once stung by a scorpion and since then, nothing has hurt her quite like a scorpion. they then talk about their lives, with james describing studying in egypt and also a concert he is about to attend. the waiter asks what they would like to order and james orders a vegetarian and tuna sushi while teresa gets rolls of her own. when the sushi comes over, they sit closer due to the placement of the meals. james asks teresa to go to a concert with her, to which she agrees. james is excited but realizes it is 3pm and leaves.

Aaron and lana have been dating for three years and aaron decides that he wants to propose to lana at a classroom where they first met. they enter the class and the professor winks at aaron, who smiles back. the lecture begins, with the main focus of the lecture being ions. near the end of the presentation, the professor asks aaron and lana to come to the front of the class for a demonstration, much to lana's confusement. at the front of the class, the ring is presented through a notebook, and after aaron gets down on his knees, the professor switches a slide with a collage of aaron and lana. just to add, both students are attending princeton university and the ring has 5 red diamonds, due to lana's eccentric style. after aaron proposes, lana has tears streaming down as she replies yes, and the class applauds. aaron and lana's friends then come into the class and lana decides to text her mother. the professor decieds it is enough excitement for one day and reminds students about a midterm the following week.

Anna is late for her flight and is rushing to get to the airport entrance. she kneels down to tie her shoe, and as she does this, a cart is rushing towards her. david sees this happening and decides to rush to help anna as he pushes anna and the cart away. anna is stunned but looks up to see the cart, then david, who she thinks is handsome. she says thanks and says that she is late to her flight. david, who has time before his next flight, agrees to help her. they get to security and take off their clothes to get through the gate. afterwards, they ruch to their gate, and while at the gate, david decides to ask anna on a date for when she gets back. she replies that shed like to go out with him and she gives him her card. anna then boards the plane and waves goodbye to david. as she sits in her seet, she hugs the plastic blanket in excitement.

Jessie and calvin are at the airport to board a return flight home. jessie is upset because she has been thinking about breaking up with calvin for a while. while at security, there is a holdup and jessie decides to complain about a conveyor belt that is broken, to which calvin expresses concern. jessie then says that she believes that they should stop seeing eachother because their personalities are incompatible. calvin attempts to remain calm. as they leave the security, they ruch to their gate, with calvin remaining quiet and jessie following behind calvin. jessie says calvin ahs nothing to say, to which calvin responds that he agrees with jessie and syas that he is sorry that he bored jessie. when they board the plane they remember that they did not get a seat together and are glad about this. before they sit down in their separate seats, jessie asks calvin to enjoy the flight, and to return her philosophy books, and calvin responds apathetically. they then sit down in their respective seats.

Ms. bianchi and ms. morrison are at a grocery store. as they come upon the cheese section, ms. bianchi propposes her sales pitch to ms. morrsion, who listens. ms. bianchi proposes that the store should incorporate her cheese, which will increase the profits in the store. ms. morrison agrees. they also talk about buying crackers and tasting the cheese, to which ms. morrison responds that the crackers are on her. near the checkout area, ms. morrison explains her concerns about the import tax on the cheese, yet ms. bianchi reassures her with the prospect of profit. ms. morrison then explains her agreement in the deal and they both check out. they then share a bottle of champagne to close the business deal.

Charlie and alma are entering class, and charlie sits with alma before the start of class in order to start a deal. charlie says that he is willing to invest half of what alma asked for. alma is the ceo of a startup, yet she wanted the full 56,000 for her company. after talking back and forth, it is decided that charlie will invest the full amount, since his group said they would be willing to do if it was necessary, and alma would not budge. they then hug after class to conclude the deal.

Alex and chloe enter a grocery store, with alex intent on proposing to her here. he blieves chloe will enjoy it because she loves surprises. as the walk in chloe notices alex's sweat and confused look, but decides not to say much about it. alex inspects the ring whil chlow is busy, yet alex seems obviously distracted. the ring has a bright band on it. as the near the checkout lane, alex decides to propose, and he takes the ring out of his wallet. once everyone realizes what is going on, people in the grocery decide to film to whole thing on their phones. at this point, alex's friends, who were waiting outside, come inside to do the same. chloe looks stunned, and responds yes, and goes in to embrace alex. the people allow alex and chloe to come ot the front of the checkout, and everyone seems excited. chloe decides to text a friend about the experience, and also expresses her joy oevr her ring. alex and chloe also discuss where they would like to celebrate their engagement.
